{"tid":1887694,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"突然要杜牙根，求救！","createTime":"2020-02-19T17:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T15:00:08.000Z","uid":287077,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b474d250f9f6673a5732f5e500d7d70dba248fd8","tid":1887694,"uid":287077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"事源右邊大牙牙痕咗幾日，仲有啲鬆動，諗住年幾冇洗牙就去book牙醫睇下。點知牙冇得洗，醫生話我隻冇乜點痛嘅大牙其實已經由補牙部分下一直蛀到落牙根，神經壞死哂，要杜牙根！<br />\n我平時都好乖刷牙洗牙，冇理由會輪到我喎！<br />\n利申我用緊學校牙科保健計劃嘅，醫生話建議我去專科做，佢只可以係試下，如果失敗都係要轉介專科。<br />\n然後我第二日再睇第二個醫生，都係大同小異，不過個醫生話都係建議睇專科，佢都係試下，成功率最高八成。佢有講多啲話因為我牙根個位已經打開咗，下面骨已經侵蝕咗，所以有啲複雜，唔保證可以成功。<br />\n身為窮l學生，人又虧又冇米，佢哋推介個專科齋杜牙根已經萬七，未包牙套，我根本負擔唔到T T<br />\n各位巴絲有冇咩經驗或建議可以分享下？<br />\n不過p牌post都係聽沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2875274e00ac2751202fafcb0cc288b590f342a","tid":1887694,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推下啊唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3366ccd82afa76f7bfede1133f0ca29d6ccafd","tid":1887694,"uid":218783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"你依家幾歲先？<br />\n我都杜過牙根嘅"},{"pid":"b64d7a5b50a50322b8f533429c21d7c2cd496213","tid":1887694,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b474d250f9f6673a5732f5e500d7d70dba248fd8"